nnoremap <LEADER>} viW<ESC>`>a}<ESC>`<i{<ESC>
nnoremap <LEADER>< viW<ESC>`>a><ESC>`<i<<ESC>
nnoremap <LEADER>> viW<ESC>`>a><ESC>`<i<<ESC>

" put stuff around selected text
